<h3 class="text-center mb-2">Instructions for paying the registration fee:</h3>
<h4 class="text-center mb-2">For individuals</h4>
<p>To pay the registration fee, you need to download the corresponding agreement for an individual and enter your personal data into it. The completed agreement (in .doc or .docx format) and a scan of the receipt for payment of the registration fee must be sent by email to Svetlana Zubova (<a href="mailto:svetazubova@gmail.com">svetazubova@gmail.com</a>). Please indicate in the subject of the letter "GenBio2024 – last name". The agreement and document signed by "Научный сервис" LLC will be issued to you upon registration for the conference.</p>

<h4 class="text-center mb-2">For legal entities</h4>
<p>To pay the registration fee, you need to download the corresponding agreement for a legal entity, enter the name of the conference participant(s) in it and submit the agreement to the accounting department for further filling in with the details of your organization. The completed agreement must be sent by email to Svetlana Zubova (<a href="mailto:svetazubova@gmail.com">svetazubova@gmail.com</a>) for approval (in case of amendments), signing by "Научный сервис" LLC and issuing an invoice for payment of the registration fee. Please indicate in the subject of the letter "GenBio2024 – last name".</p>

